Friday, 04 October 2013

Show Description

From the Infowars web site :: On this Friday, October 4 edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex breaks down the media spin and government lies surrounding the execution of 34-year-old Miriam Carey by D.C. Capital Police. 

Investment broker and financial commentator Peter Schiff joins the show to reveal that the Federal Reserve's monetary expansion program, called Quantitative Easing, is destroying the middle class and pushing the American economy towards a cliff under the illusion of an economic recovery. 

Alex also invites author and social analyst Mark Dice on the show to talk about his latest video showcasing Obama supporters who do not even know the president is a Democrat. 

Additionally, author and psychological warfare expert Dr. Steve Pieczenik joins the broadcast to speak on the recent shooting in D.C. and the current state of the world.
